block docs
  h1 Accordion
  p Accordions toggle the visibility of content.

  p For avoiding to add a script, the open/close behavior is direclty managed from the
    |  #[code &lt;details&gt;] element.
    br
    | By adding the #[code open] attribute on the main element, the component will
    |  be opened by default.

  .p-example
    details.c-accordion.u-mb-2(open)
      summary.c-accordion__header Section 1
      .c-accordion__body
        ul.o-list-bare.u-mb-0
          li.u-py-1.u-pl-3
            a(href="#") Subsectionn 1.1
          li.u-py-1.u-pl-3
            a(href="#") Subsectionn 1.2
          li.u-py-1.u-pl-3
            a(href="#") Subsectionn 1.3
    details.c-accordion.u-mb-2
