  p The accordion module also can be combined with other component, like the card for example:

  .p-example
    details.c-card.c-accordion.u-mb-3
      summary.c-card__header.c-accordion__header.u-py-2 You have a question?
      .c-card__body.c-accordion__body We an a super answer for you!
    details.c-card.c-accordion
